Requirements:
============


To display a map and plot points on the map, tapping/clicking on point will display a list of events
Use Node.js and MongDB to feed the data
An admin side will be able to add /edit/ delete markers
Cache the data into localStorage rather than on the fly after selecting each marker
Map will centre on the devices location. 



Routes:
=======

/
goes to index.html

/markers
 lists markers in json format
